snippet.title: Phoenix Point Teaser
snippet.description:
Phoenix Point is the new strategy game from the creator of the original X-COM series. Visit our website at http://www.phoenixpoint.info to subscribe to our newsletter.

Music & Sound by John Broomhall http://www.johnbroomhall.co.uk
John composed the music for the original X-COM game in released in 1994.
